sph.vaadin.ui.videojs

Interface Videojs.VjsListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EventListener<String,Videojs,Double>, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    Videojs

    public static interface Videojs.VjsListener
extends EventListener<String,Videojs,Double>
    EventListener interface for listening to client side Video.js Events delegated to and fired by a Videojs player component.
    Since:
    11.10.2013
    Version:
    2.01
    Author:
    Sami Holck, Juha Mäkilä

      • on

        void on(String eventName,
      Videojs source,
      Double triggerTime)
        Videojs Component has triggered an event.
        Specified by:
        on in interface EventListener<String,Videojs,Double>
        Parameters:
        eventName - name of the VideojsListener event.
        source - the source component of the VideojsListener event.
        triggerTime - the playback time of the videostream when the event is triggered.
